title: EYES ON PAC-12
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Harry Lyles Jr, discuss a rough start to the for the PAC 12. The PAC 12 went 6-6 in Week 1, but looking to make a bounce back in Week 2 with some marquee matchups.
